        p Mai/2014
      .work-title
        a(target="_blank" href="http://www.hugeinc.com/")
          p.company Huge Inc
        p.title Developer
      .work-description
        p Huge is an agency focused on developing digital solutions capable of delivering good experiences and improving people’s quality of life. At the agency the deliverables were high fidelity prototypes and I started out as an intern working on those prototypes. From Jade (HTML) and Sass (CSS), the projects started getting more complicated and we could experiment with other tools, such as
          a(href="https://harpjs.com/")  HarpJS
          | ,
          a(href="https://gruntjs.com/")  Grunt
          | ,
          a(href="https://gulpjs.com/")  Gulp
          | . I got involved with over 5 projects, including
          a(target="_blank" href="http://www.riogaleao.com/")  Galeão International Airport
          | , shopping center company
          a(target="_blank" href="http://www.barrashopping.com.br/")  Multiplan
          |  and pro-bono donation platform
          a(target="_blank" href="http://www.e-solidario.com.br/index.xhtml")  E-Solidario
          | . Other than my proper job, I also ran an
          i  English Club
          | , lunch-time-gatherings during which only English was allowed. We would talk about any subject as long as it was in English, so everyone would get some practice.
        ul.tools
          li(title="Javascript") JS (JQuery)
          li HTML (Pug)
          li CSS (Sass)
          li Git
          li Gulp
          li Grunt
          li HarpJS
          li Node

